OL,6,GThey say Christmas comes earlier every
OL,7,Gyear. But when it comes to the BBC News
OL,8,Gon BBC One, there's never been
OL,9,Gconsistency to holiday scheduling.
OL,11,FThis year, the BBC started to move
OL,12,Ftowards a holiday schedule unusually
OL,13,Fearly.
OL,15,FOn 21st December, the BBC News at Six
OL,16,Fand the regional programmes were
OL,17,Fcurtailed because of Sports Personality
OL,18,Fof the Year ` pushed from its normal
OL,19,FSunday night slot by the World Cup.
OL,3,CTime to rethink the Christmas
OL,4,Ccurtailing of BBC One news?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G1/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
