OL,6,FThere was to be no regional news and
OL,7,FNationwide. Instead the regions were to
OL,8,Fbe allowed to opt out of The Clangers
OL,9,Fat 5.35pm for a brief bulletin. At 6pm
OL,10,FEBC 1 with Rod Hull and Emu was due to
OL,11,Fair.
OL,13,FThe periods between Christmas and New
OL,14,FYear have also witnessed changing
OL,15,Fattitudes towards news over the years.
OL,17,FIn the late-80s, there were occasions
OL,18,Fwhen all the main national and regional
OL,19,Fbulletins were shown as usual on any
OL,20,Fweekdays between the 27th and 30th.
OL,3,CTime to rethink the Christmas
OL,4,Ccurtailing of BBC One news?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G4/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
