OL,6,FIn recent years, there seems to have
OL,7,Fbeen a slow trend back towards this.
OL,9,FThis year the BBC News at Ten will run
OL,10,Ffrom the 28th to 30th. The BBC News at
OL,11,FOne returns on the 27th but is
OL,12,Fdisplaced by five minutes on Friday.
OL,14,FHowever the 6pm hour is substantially
OL,15,Fshorter and displaced to 6.15pm.
OL,17,FIt is time to end all this.
OL,19,FBBC News is well-resourced and at the
OL,20,Fcentre of the flagship channel's
OL,21,Fschedule.
OL,3,CTime to rethink the Christmas
OL,4,Ccurtailing of BBC One news?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G5/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34606
