OL,6,FProgrammes should run as normal until
OL,7,Fthe 23rd and on any weekday between the
OL,8,F27th and 30th.
OL,10,FThe staffing issues which may have
OL,11,Fexplained the issues in days of old are
OL,12,Fgone.
OL,14,FIf the English regions are unable to
OL,15,Fprovide a full service, it should not
OL,16,Fstop Scotland, Wales and Northern
OL,17,FIreland. Network schedules can allow
OL,18,Ffor this.
OL,3,CTime to rethink the Christmas
OL,4,Ccurtailing of BBC One news?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G6/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34607
