OL,6,FQuiet days should not be an issue
OL,7,Feither. Any news bulletin includes
OL,8,Fpieces commissioned in advance. On
OL,9,Fquiet days, middle-ranking stories gain
OL,10,Fin status.
OL,12,FITV is running its normal morning
OL,13,Fschedule between Christmas and New Year
OL,14,F` presumably in the belief they will
OL,15,Frate better than festive films and
OL,16,Ffillers.
OL,18,FIt's time for the BBC to do the same
OL,19,Fwith its principle news programmes.
OL,3,CTime to rethink the Christmas
OL,4,Ccurtailing of BBC One news?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G7/7
